About Oxford Fashion Institute

Established in 1999, Oxford Fashion Institute has been Kerala's leading provider of professional fashion education and training services for over two decades.

We specialize in comprehensive fashion design programs, industry certifications, and professional development services. Our expert faculty and modern facilities ensure students receive world-class education that prepares them for successful careers in the fashion industry.

With over 500 successful graduates placed in top fashion companies worldwide, we maintain a 95% success rate in career placement and professional development.
